name: Add a signature block to a new document
fullName: features/document_creation.feature#Add a signature block to a new document

steps.name: I am on the New Beta Editor page
When I click on New Document
And I click on the Signatures tab
Then I should see a signature block
And I drag the signature block to the right edge of the document

labels.name: suite
labels.value: Add a signature block to a new document
